	(text "0A -> 5V\nPick 6A as max current for short detection. Ignitors should pull 3-4A.\nVout_max = REF + 6A * Rsense * Gain\n          = 0 + 6 * 0.01 * 50\n          = 3V\nAt 0A, output should be 0V\n\nI_IGN = V_out / (0.01 * 50)"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 16.002 185.42 0)
		(effects
